name: KayipKux's Basics 3 - The Future
description:
I know, i know, its been a few months since i havent worked on KB3... But it's finally here.

Story

Basically, Kayip still hasn't got his revenge yet! So after you escaped the old school, he took you to the future, and this time to escape is a LOT more difficult. Because there's more characters, more chaos. Good luck.

Roles

1st Prize - Withered 1st Prize

Have fun playing this!
